article_title: Conflicting reports about number of babies evacuated from al-Shifa.
sentence: "But  unfortunately  one  baby  died  yesterday,  and  another  died  this  morning,  [so]  we  had  to  move  the  remaining  31  babies  to  the  Emirati  Hospital  in  the  southern  city  of  Rafah,"  she  explained.
